   "source": [
    "# LaTeX and APL\n",
    "### LaTeX formatted formulas with Dyalog APL                                  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Let's do sum and product:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Sum of numbers from 1 to 100:\n",
    "$$\\sum_{n=1}^{100}x_n$$\n",
    "in APL:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<span style=\"white-space:pre; font-family: monospace\">5050\n",
       "</span>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 1,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "+/⍳100"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Product of numbers from 1 to 100:\n",
    "$$\\prod_{n=1}^{100}x_n$$\n",
    "in APL:"
   ]
  },
  {
